
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Image Gallery - Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <style>
        /* General styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-image: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/1568607/pexels-photo-1568607.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1'); /* Replace 'path/to/your/image.jpg' with the actual path to your image */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; /* Align items from top to bottom */
            min-height: 100vh; /* Ensure the body takes up at least the full height of the viewport */
            justify-content: center; /* Center content vertically */
            align-items: center; /* Center content horizontally */
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4); /* Add a semi-transparent white background for better readability */
            border-radius: 20px; /* Add rounded corners to the container */
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Form styles */
        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column; /* Arrange items vertically */
            align-items: center;
        }

        input[type="file"] {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        button[type="submit"] {
            width: 50%;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        button[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        /* View gallery button */
        .view-gallery-button {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #007bff;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: rgb(78, 245, 78);
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .view-gallery-button:hover {
            background-color: #ddd;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Our Image Gallery</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section class="intro">
            <p><i>Introducing our latest innovation in visual storytelling: the Image Gallery. Seamlessly designed to showcase your cherished moments, artistic creations, and unforgettable memories, our Image Gallery is a digital canvas where your images come to life.</i></p>
            
        </section>

       

        <section class="upload-form">
            <h2>Upload Your Image</h2>
            <form action="/upload" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
                <input type="file" name="image" accept="image/*" required>
                <button type="submit">Upload</button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section class="view-gallery">
            <a href="/gallery" class="view-gallery-button">View Gallery</a>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Image Gallery. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>

